&lt;p&gt;The Correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Krunal Pandya&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;color: (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Krunal Pandya&lt;/strong&gt; was awarded the &lt;strong&gt;Player of the Match&lt;/strong&gt; for his exceptional performance in both the &lt;strong&gt;2017 IPL final&lt;/strong&gt; and the &lt;strong&gt;2025 IPL final.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In the &lt;strong&gt;2017 IPL final&lt;/strong&gt;, Krunal Pandya played a crucial role for the &lt;strong&gt;Mumbai Indians&lt;/strong&gt; against the &lt;strong&gt;Rising Pune Supergiant&lt;/strong&gt;. His all-round performance helped his team secure the title.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;His contributions included a &lt;strong&gt;match-winning knock&lt;/strong&gt; with the bat and impactful bowling, which turned the tide in favor of his team.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In the &lt;strong&gt;2025 IPL final&lt;/strong&gt;, Krunal Pandya once again displayed his &lt;strong&gt;all-round brilliance&lt;/strong&gt;, contributing significantly with both the bat and ball to help his team clinch another title.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Krunal Pandya&amp;#39;s ability to perform under pressure in high-stakes matches has earned him recognition as one of the most reliable all-rounders in the IPL.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;His consistent performances in finals have made him a valuable asset for his team and a celebrated player in the IPL history.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The achievement of being named &lt;strong&gt;Player of the Match&lt;/strong&gt; in two IPL finals demonstrates his &lt;strong&gt;versatility&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;match-winning capability&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hardik Pandya&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hardik Pandya&lt;/strong&gt; is also a renowned all-rounder in the IPL. He has delivered impactful performances for teams like &lt;strong&gt;Mumbai Indians&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Gujarat Titans.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Although Hardik has played crucial roles in various matches, he was not awarded the &lt;strong&gt;Player of the Match&lt;/strong&gt; in both the &lt;strong&gt;2017&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;2025 IPL finals.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rohit Sharma&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rohit Sharma&lt;/strong&gt; is the captain of the &lt;strong&gt;Mumbai Indians&lt;/strong&gt;, the most successful team in IPL history.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;He has led his team to multiple IPL titles and is known for his &lt;strong&gt;calm leadership&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;batting prowess.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Though Rohit has been instrumental in IPL finals, he was not declared &lt;strong&gt;Player of the Match&lt;/strong&gt; in the &lt;strong&gt;2017&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;2025 IPL finals.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Virat Kohli&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Virat Kohli&lt;/strong&gt; is one of the most celebrated players in IPL history and has played for the &lt;strong&gt;Royal Challengers Bangalore.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Despite his remarkable batting records and achievements, he was not awarded the &lt;strong&gt;Player of the Match&lt;/strong&gt; in the &lt;strong&gt;2017&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;2025 IPL finals.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Taloja, Navi Mumbai.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Maharashtra Chief Minister Devendra Fadnavis and former Chief Justice of India Justice Bhushan R. Gavai inaugurated India&amp;rsquo;s first Bharat Ratna Dr Babasaheb Ambedkar Advocate Training and Research Centre (BBATRC) at Taloja, Navi Mumbai.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The BBATRC has been established by the Maharashtra and Goa Bar Council.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The Centre aims to bridge the gap between legal education and practical courtroom training.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The inauguration was presided over by the Chief Justice of the Bombay High Court, Justice Shree Chandrashekhar.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Other dignitaries present included Chief Justice of Meghalaya High Court Justice Revati Mohite-Dere, Additional Solicitor General of India Anil C. Singh, Maharashtra Advocate General Dr Milind Sathe, and Goa Advocate General Devidas Pangam.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Bharat Ratna Dr Babasaheb Ambedkar Advocate Training and Research Centre (BBATRC)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;India&amp;rsquo;s first centre dedicated to advanced legal training and research for advocates.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Focuses on enhancing courtroom skills and bridging the divide between theoretical legal education and practical practice.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Named in honour of Dr B.R. Ambedkar, Bharat Ratna awardee and principal architect of the Indian Constitution.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Significance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Strengthens the legal profession and promotes continuous skill development for advocates.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Provides a platform for research, training, and development in law and legal practice.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Surakshit Tat, Samridh Bharat.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Central Industrial Security Force organised the 2nd edition of the Vande Mataram Coastal Cyclothon 2026 with the theme &amp;ldquo;Surakshit Tat, Samridh Bharat&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The official theme of the Vande Mataram Coastal Cyclothon 2026 is Surakshit Tat, Samridh Bharat.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The cyclothon is part of the commemoration of 150 years of Vande Mataram.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The 25-day event aims to strengthen coastal security awareness and national unity.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The initiative also promotes fitness, discipline and community participation among coastal populations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Vande Mataram Coastal Cyclothon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Organised by the Central Industrial Security Force&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Aims to promote coastal security awareness and patriotism&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Engages coastal communities and youth across India&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Central Industrial Security Force&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Functions under the Ministry of Home Affairs&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Provides security to critical infrastructure including ports and airports&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Recognised under the International Ship and Port Facility Security Code&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;150 Years of Vande Mataram&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Marks the anniversary of the iconic patriotic song&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Celebrated through nationwide events and initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Focuses on patriotism and national consciousness&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

